  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Exocraft Survey Device",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "强化艇调查设备",
    "TraditionalChinese": "強化艇調查裝置"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "An enhancement to the Exocraft's navigational capabilities, attaching to the driver's visor display. Analyses surroundings and projects detailed data over the environment, identifying <span class=\"name name-stellar\">points of interest</span> and generating <span class=\"name name-commodity\">valuable data</span> when used to study <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">flora</span>, <span class=\"name name-fuel\">fauna</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">minerals</span>.<br><br>Hold <span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span> to operate.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "对强化艇导航系统的一项改进，该改进装置安装在驾驶员的面甲上。它能分析周围环境，并将详细数据投射到环境中，从而识别<span class=\"name name-stellar\">兴趣点</span>并将这些<span class=\"name name-commodity\">有价值的数据</span>用于研究<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">植物群系</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">动物群系</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">矿物</span>。<br><br>按下<span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span>运行。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "加強強化艇的導航功能，並可連接至駕駛者的護目鏡顯示器。能分析周圍環境，並將詳細資料投射到環境中，以辨識<span class=\"name name-stellar\">重要地點</span>並生成<span class=\"name name-commodity\">珍貴資料</span>，可用於研究<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">植物</span>、<span class=\"name name-fuel\">動物</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">礦物</span>。<br><br>按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">AIM</span> 以操作。"
  },
